    "TraditionalChinese": "找出奈米機群"
  },
  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "A strange and potent substance, <span class=\"name name-technology\">nanite clusters</span> are found where the boundaries of the universe weaken. Seek <VAL_ON>abandoned buildings<> and other sites of interest.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "在宇宙边界被削弱的地方，发现了一种奇怪而强大的物质，<span class=\"name name-technology\">纳米星团</span>。寻找<VAL_ON>废弃建筑<>和其他感兴趣的地点。",
    "TencentChinese": "在宇宙边界被削弱的地方，发现了一种奇怪而强大的物质，<span class=\"name name-technology\">纳米星团</span>。寻找<VAL_ON>废弃建筑<>和其他感兴趣的地点。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "宇宙邊界消弱處可見<span class=\"name name-technology\">奈米機群</span>，是一種奇怪又高效的物質。尋找<VAL_ON>廢棄建築物<>與其他重要地點。"
  },
